      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARG'S VOGUE (4) is a quick beginner who bombed the start last time and missed the frame, finishing seventh (22.91) in a Grade 3/4 at Gosford. Fast away and won (22.91) at Gosford the start prior. Has a good record here including five wins. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Tough to beat if on-song. SMART COMET (3) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4 lengths (23.32) at this track. Speedy beginner who should be prominent early on from an inside box. Likely to be about the mark. SHANGHAI SPY (2) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
